!!【柯林斯英汉双解大词典】

:<div>

recreation /ˌrɛkrɪˈeɪʃən/

(recreations) 

1. N-VAR Recreation consists of things that you do in your spare time to relax. 娱乐 

例： Saturday afternoon is for recreation and outings. 周六下午是娱乐和外出的时间。 

2. N-COUNT A recreation of something is the process of making it exist or seem to exist again in a different time or place. 重现; 重建 

例： They are planning to build a faithful recreation of the original frontier town. 他们正计划建造一座和原来边境城镇一模一样的复制品。

</div>

